content:
Create Flexible and Dynamic Sales Packages

Add products to a bundle when you configure a product. Sales reps can now search and add qualified products to a bundle in real-time, and create flexible and customized sales packages. Additionally, sales reps can add the same product multiple times with a unique name-attribute identifier.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Developer, Enterprise, and Unlimited editions where Revenue Lifecycle Management and Product Configurator are enabled.
title: Salesforce Summer '24 Release Notes: Enhanced Sales Packages
